<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Home Finds and our affiliate relationships.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-8">About Home Finds</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray prose-lg">
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>Home Finds</strong> — your curated destination for the best home and kitchen products. We believe that a beautiful, functional home starts with the right tools and decor.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our team scours the market to find products that combine quality, design, and value. From innovative kitchen gadgets to cozy living room decor and clever organization solutions, every product on this site has been handpicked with care.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We want to make it easy for you to discover products that enhance your home. Whether you're an avid home cook, a decor enthusiast, or someone looking to get organized, we've got you covered.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Home Finds is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to <a href="https://www.amazon.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. This means that if you click on a link to a product on our site and make a purchase on Amazon, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our editorial content is not influenced by our affiliate relationships. We only recommend products we genuinely believe in.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you. Reach out to us at <strong>hello@homefinds.com</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
